main event: A cigar-shaped UFO was observed by multiple military personnel in Cyprus on July 6, 1965.
interesting points: The object was observed simultaneously from three different locations on the island of Cyprus.
The object was estimated to be at an altitude of 159,000 feet.
The object's speed was estimated to be around 45 knots.
The object appeared to be circular from underneath and cone-shaped from the side.
The object was estimated to be approximately the same size as a 3,000-ton ship.
